=== Loi giai tu luan ===

Thong so: n = 8, k = 4, r = 4
g(x) = x^4 + x + 1

STT  m(bin)      m(x)           c(bin)
------------------------------------------------------------
0    0000        0              00000000
1    0001        x^3            10011000
2    0010        x^2            01001100
3    0011        x^3 + x^2      11010100
4    0100        x              00100110
5    0101        x^3 + x        10111110
6    0110        x^2 + x        01101010
7    0111        x^3 + x^2 + x  11110010
...
15   1111        x^3 + x^2 + x + 111100001

Ket qua: d_min = 3, phat hien 2 loi, sua 1 loi
